{"tid":1900092,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"《蘋果日報》傳裁員至少40人","createTime":"2020-02-27T04:25:23.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-28T02:42:10.000Z","uid":184679,"like":10,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":29,"replies":[{"pid":"2f41c0b8393b77970afd91b67598c4ed76eeee31","tid":1900092,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-27T04:25:23.000Z","msg":"本地傳媒報道，壹傳媒 （00282） 旗下香港《蘋果日報》近日裁員至少40人，被裁員工將於本月底離職，主要涉及印刷及數碼業務部門。<br />\n<br />\n消息指，因新冠肺炎衝擊廣告業務，《蘋果日報》印刷業務及數碼業務的營業部門合併，並裁逾20人；另外，去年推出的短片平台「一丁目」傳全組解散。<br />\n<br />\n有指壹傳媒工會接獲員工求助，主要涉及營業和市場部，並不涉及編採部門人員。<br />\n<br />\n<pre><code data-type=\"\">https://inews.hket.com/article/2575770/%E3%80%8A%E8%98%8B%E6%9E%9C%E6%97%A5%E5%A0%B1%E3%80%8B%E5%82%B3%E8%A3%81%E5%93%A1%E8%87%B3%E5%B0%9140%E4%BA%BA</code></pre>"},{"pid":"e30ccdfd27a656b69256699fcfb641befa7853d7","tid":1900092,"uid":11148,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-27T04:28:24.000Z","msg":"咁多人課金都唔掂 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"448ff8c751e7c4d87e9e35f1c543185095777a26","tid":1900092,"uid":229183,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-27T04:29:06.000Z","msg":"黑警為了有258億撥款 搞到市民冇得拿1萬 黑警搞到大家攬炒"},{"pid":"2894da0b66c07e2458a9fc76d0d0c2cf0fb226cb","tid":1900092,"uid":229656,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-27T04:29:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"043fc72d5777925b77b4a389670926a7e6ef55be","tid":1900092,"uid":350689,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-27T04:29:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7d21e34a9b8d0024c170dfd39e99b952b9d5ad32","tid":1900092,"uid":40267,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-27T04:30:11.000Z","msg":"唔係掛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/fac